{"tid":1466162,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"道乜嘢歉啊道？","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:14:49.000Z","uid":299389,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8873cd1715592aecfbe0cb60fe89359c27d94d65","tid":1466162,"uid":299389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">如果係道歉，DAY ONE就已經要道歉啦係咪呀？一陣又話阻住返工，<br />\n一陣又話搞lum香港經濟，<br />\n一陣又話破壞香港和平，<br />\n一陣又話失民意、破壞形象。<br />\n<br />\n船頭驚鬼， 船尾驚賊<br />\n乜都驚乜都介意嘅，就乜嘢都唔好做啦！<br />\n唔做咪唔會錯。但呢個係咪真係你想要嘅嘢？<br />\n坦白講，<br />\n第一，無論你做乜都一定會有人反對。<br />\n第二，No pay no gain. 無付出無收穫。<br />\n你嘅付出可能都要忍受犧牲小部分人嘅利益。<br />\n但呢個世界一向都係咁運作。<br />\n第三，世界上最貴嘅嘢係用錢買唔到，<br />\n例如自由。<br />\n呢d道理人人都明。<br />\n你係做大事嘅，就唔好乜都顧忌。<br />\n<br />\n最後，道歉無問題，<br />\n問題係我地究竟係咪真係做錯？<br />\n<br />\n如果你有睇今晚Now TV深宵新聞<br />\n有個係機場嘅香港auntie話：<br />\n道歉唔係大曬！<br />\n<br />\n所以你嘅道歉有可能turn out 令人覺得你根本就係錯，錯到貼曬地，而家咪死死地氣出黎認錯。<br />\n但都唔否認有小數人會接受道歉。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">切勿濫用道歉。</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0d11b8999d5f0239880ded05de6bd6fda2d603f","tid":1466162,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"文宣：打人搞事個班係臥底<br />\n要連埋早幾日個堆臥底現真身既證據<br />\n強調呢招係共匪一貫套路！<br />\n<br />\n中英文多國語言版<br />\n<br />\n求下你地，唔可以輸！"},{"pid":"0750490e53c038365ae9835c49275896ea662ae7","tid":1466162,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc04470e49f0bed6c53e74c03ef777c90d015a67","tid":1466162,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"不割蓆，各有各做"},{"pid":"54113a37c586178aed02b6f6bab03d9476149e0e","tid":1466162,"uid":299389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽實，<br />\n如果堅持要道歉，會支持到底。<br />\n<br />\n不分化、不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"9536f18a83d4b18020da4fb2d4d7ee3a36ac8b6f","tid":1466162,"uid":219110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"唔道歉同林鄭同埋D狗有咩分別"},{"pid":"025ea7edb78016fe95450818ff0a299bf732036b","tid":1466162,"uid":299389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9536f18a83d4b18020da4fb2d4d7ee3a36ac8b6f","tid":1466162,"uid":219110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"唔道歉同林鄭同埋D狗有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"無人叫你唔道歉，但唔好下下都認曬低威，咩嘢都係自己錯。如果道歉活動成日搞，請問價值係邊？"},{"pid":"ee71be1129c741f61c96a1409c91c3c713b656ce","tid":1466162,"uid":299389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc04470e49f0bed6c53e74c03ef777c90d015a67","tid":1466162,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"不割蓆，各有各做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Agger</span></span>"},{"pid":"e5bb331467e75da9fb7c6f3eabc76fdd67046a3b","tid":1466162,"uid":299389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"35c84eb09bab1737586992e91504edb75aecfb09","tid":1466162,"uid":299389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"推到全世界都睇到為止"},{"pid":"c96cc4c737ccda1b808adb84da09b1c43b99dea4","tid":1466162,"uid":299389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse